This harbour (called "Cibotus," <I>i.e.</I>Â "Chest" or "Box"), which was fortified, was connected with Lake Mareotis by a canal. Its shape and size are toâ€‘day problematical, for it


<A ID="p27x"></A>has been filled up and its site lies within that of the present Heptastadium.


